1) cl
Clears the screen

2) echo <text>
Prints text

3) cf <folder_name>
Creates a directory

4) rf <folder_name>
Removes a directories

5) ct <file_name> = <text>
Creates a file

6) rt <file_name>
Removes a file

7) lf <file_name>
Read a file

8) ls
List files and directories

9) cd <folder_name> | cd ..
Enter a directory | Go back a directory
